Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}おっ もう時間か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‪（原田）あと２勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‪２勝か…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‪（太一）んっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‪（千早）原田先生は\N‪準決勝で惜敗
